text:
The first step is to implement link records: InteractiveInfoAtom and
ExHyperlinkAtom.  

As for API it should be simple. Link is an attribute of a text run.
A sample use case may look as follows:

TextRun run = ..;
Hyperlink link = run.getHyperlink();
String href = link.getAddress(); 
String title = link.getTitle();

//setting a link: 
Hyperlink link = new Hyperlink();
link.setAddress("jakarta.apache.org");
link.setTitle("Jakarta Apache");

run.setHyperlink(link);
or
run.setHyperlink(link, startIdx, endIdx); 

Let's start with the atoms. 

Yegor
